{"tid":1640540,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"行動post! 全港大型office區lunchtime慶雙十, Stand with Taiwan!","createTime":"2019-10-09T04:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T03:11:34.000Z","uid":265872,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b47458ef23b21335129910d614fc098175495590","tid":1640540,"uid":265872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"聽日係台灣雙十國慶, 中共黨慶係国殤, 但台灣雙十真係要歡賀呀!<br />\n為表香港人對台灣既祝賀, 聽日麻煩所有會返工既手足, 晌各大型office區和平集結或行街街, stand with Taiwan, 同埋香港人唔係反中華文化呀, 係討厭你個共產黨咋!<br />\n必備配件: 各式口罩; 台灣國旗/島旗/鲸魚旗<br />\n其他如示威牌呀, 氣球呀, 甚至台灣NBA林書豪!大家發揮創意啦~~<br />\n路線各區自己定, 但希望和理優, 同分區唔好太細令人數太少,並選擇人多既大街, its celebration, 要同食lunch既香港人同慶 (不排除popo會唔會放tg幫大家放半日假?)"},{"pid":"166943a66d37a64b2c3ea41fa1fb8046de64cb94","tid":1640540,"uid":265872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:07:45.000Z","msg":"Push by myself"},{"pid":"062c7b1f96541dde6fc0c3256ef75ef48f857331","tid":1640540,"uid":265872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"Push 2"},{"pid":"8289751c89410f6b4dfa4e219f6be495558d8075","tid":1640540,"uid":265872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:08:10.000Z","msg":"Push 3"},{"pid":"c533ae5fa022beedd63b73435ca3e5f6433bc01b","tid":1640540,"uid":314629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b165f1e493225649bd4c7e0b0634dbfb3e56f62","tid":1640540,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2efdba106ebec33a56481ac8ec86c4fd4a20ed45","tid":1640540,"uid":3127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:32:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88d9053a654a8dffdf18d0243e4159d287bded31","tid":1640540,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse